{"tid":1315317,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮聯署破10萬，促國會通過《香港人權及民主法案》","createTime":"2019-07-14T13:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T08:07:18.000Z","uid":278587,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"96ca4cfdefdf7e44acf23130dcf5d25a90a9686c","tid":1315317,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3032328/org/6e4d487e4721384eea64439d1afd0756.png/YpnQvgOMmV_baRUtzIrONws_8V8PeREM60Zkt-tGZLc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3032328%2Forg%2F6e4d487e4721384eea64439d1afd0756.png%2FYpnQvgOMmV_baRUtzIrONws_8V8PeREM60Zkt-tGZLc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=c8b116ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反對《逃犯條例》修訂浪潮持續，引起國際社會廣泛報導。有網民於上周一(8日)發起白宮聯署，要求美國國會通過《香港人權及民主法案》。議題在不足一週內成功取得10萬人聯署，達到白宮官方回應的門檻。<br />\n<br />\n網民J.J於7月8日於美國白宮網頁發起題為「要求通過《香港人權及民主法案》」的聯署，內容指香港正面臨人權倒退的情況，香港高度自治的承諾被忽視違背，促請美方通過法案確保香港的高度自治，支持港人爭取與美國同等的人權。<br />\n<br />\n今次並非首次有網民在白宮網頁發起反修例聯署，早在六月有網民發起白宮聯署促請美國就修例發表意見，審視與香港簽訂的引渡條約，當時亦成功取得10萬人聯署。<br />\n<br />\n美國前總統奧巴馬於政府於2011年設立「We The People」網站，市民可就不同議題開設聯署運動，當聯署在30天內達到10萬個簽名或以上這個目標，白宮會就議題作出官方回應。不過，自美國總統特朗普上台後，有多達七項聯署即使到達10萬人簽名，但白宮在今年1月起已沒有就任何達標聯署回應。"},{"pid":"f56d7b9247cc593945fcd05b06f49aba84f96b53","tid":1315317,"uid":260367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:33:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4f1286279385574916d0a557677ccec0e009574","tid":1315317,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T00:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b7ec14bb2566f19d40fa72ebae30f2bfb5a1ef","tid":1315317,"uid":63927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:49:57.000Z","msg":"簽埋呢個，要求美國政府調查中共組織：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/federal-government-must-investigate-organizations-set-chinese-communist-promote-their-political-agenda?fbclid=IwAR1Mh6T5yuHT7SH0VdyRs_BltbP0d9WilFd5u8NTCU1G-zBw9X6GgjKFn7E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Ffederal-government-must-investigate-organizations-set-chinese-communist-promote-their-political-agenda%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Mh6T5yuHT7SH0VdyRs_BltbP0d9WilFd5u8NTCU1G-zBw9X6GgjKFn7E&d=uli%2BLK8ypwQfiBTSi%2FGP9yMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=341ec0f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/federal-government-must-investigate-organizations-set-chinese-communist-promote-their-political-agenda?fbclid=IwAR1Mh6T5yuHT7SH0VdyRs_BltbP0d9WilFd5u8NTCU1G-zBw9X6GgjKFn7E</a>"},{"pid":"65cd768ab7309bfe2c9bfacb5b939e08fa56a03f","tid":1315317,"uid":261819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T21:48:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3248660d8ddd42db267662764040d9e8b72cf216","tid":1315317,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:24:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3db14d59f99930be1914fddf62e11e70d7ca9b0b","tid":1315317,"uid":199838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}